{"tid":1993640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 登記選民 最後4日","createTime":"2020-04-29T01:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T02:19:03.000Z","uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04bc6d72fb8f3d8e95af2d260bf7849ec6bbc825","tid":1993640,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLNQtfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLNQtfZ.jpg&h=5ec3b0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#登記選民 最後4日‼️<br />\n<br />\n【做左選民登記未？點樣登記？】<br />\n➡️檢查是否已登記做選民<br />\n（包括 立法會地方選區 及 功能界別）<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=357f8346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n➡️地方選區選民新登記申請表<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=6d12f9f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n（新登記地方選區選民將自動成為功能界別：區議會（第二）選民）<br />\n<br />\n➡️功能界別選民新登記申請表<br />\n（適用於申請成為區議會（第二）/專業界別 選民）<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=0c84bee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n➡️遞交方式<br />\n👉🏻郵寄（九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓）<br />\n👉🏻傳真（2891 1180）<br />\n👉🏻電郵方式（form@reo.gov.hk）<br />\n👉🏻上傳至政府網上平台（<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Fupload_form_reo1.jsp&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=63566629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp</a> (<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Fupload_form_reo1.jsp&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=63566629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp</a>)）<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 每名選民可享有最多兩張個人票（地方選區、功能組別）及一張公司票（團體選民）<br />\n#立法會 #選舉 #選民登記"},{"pid":"f73db3c66a70c6aaea7f108baf2a13a640bd9af3","tid":1993640,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13d52f10fc84b47a7cec6556c4a0ccbefb674060","tid":1993640,"uid":189132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975c14cc771e0acf0738763e3427d9a7be53f1da","tid":1993640,"uid":72361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}